### Alle Einträge abrufen (Admin: alle, Reporter: eigene)
GET {{host}}/entry
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Eintrag erstellen
POST {{host}}/entry
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "kitId": "f9ec2188-288e-44c5-9043-8f267fc5004b",
  "occurredAt": "2026-02-12T08:30:00.000Z",
  "incident": "Schnittverletzung",
  "description": "Schnittverletzung am Finger in der Werkstatt",
